    Canopy Cove

    We are thrilled to announce the exciting expansion of our Student Care premises in the vibrant Tiong Bahru neighborhood! Introducing the all-new 'Canopy Cove,' a space carefully designed to provide a warm and welcoming atmosphere for our students. This expansion not only represents our commitment to their well-being but also aims to enhance their overall learning experience.

    Book a centre tour!

    Our Programmes

    Student Care

    For ages 7 - 12 years old

    We offer quality after-school care that is intentional in the development of each childs acquisition of knowledge, skills, and values. The program will provide academic rigour, outdoor activities, enrichment courses and regular workshops.

    Holiday Programmes

    For ages 7 -12 years old

    Enjoy unforgettable, memorable programmes at Canopy Student Care every time during the school holidays! We collaborate with programme experts to craft unique programmes for enriching experiences and personal development.

    Our Vision

    An Canopy, our vision is clear. We see the lack of holistic, comprehensive after-school care and through an inclusive Student Care and Holistic Education, focusing on their overall well-bring and growth. We aim to nurture not only academic success but also personal development, character-building, and discovering one's purpose. 

    What our Parents say

    "My girl had been at Canopy for 3-4 years until she finally graduated last year but still dearly missed all the nice teachers at Canopy! Teachers at Canopy are responsible, caring and will always update parents on the well-being of our child from time to time. They too provide a very cohesive learning environment with mini library/reading corner with variety of books, displaying the students' art & craft etc. Thanks for nurturing my girl for the past few years and seeing her grown up to be a sensible young lady."

    Aly, parent of P6 student

    "I like that the teachers are very caring at Canopy and at Canopy, there is a good balance of outdoor play and academic support. My child looks forward to the outdoor play every week and he also looks forward to the exciting holiday programmes that the student care plans for them during the school holidays. Meals are healthy and the facilities are clean. Overall a great experience!"

    Xin Yi, parent of P2 student

A holistic student care that takes care of and monitors my child's development and needs.
